main event: An observer sighted a bright red object which transformed into two white objects in Cincinnati, Ohio, in 1967.
interesting points: The observer described the object as a round circle,The motion of the objects was erratic and there was no discernible pattern,The encounter lasted approximately 30 minutes,The observer reported that the object passed behind clouds and changed colors,There was an instance of another similar unreported UFO sighting in the area.
sighted object: a bright red object that changed color to white
witness description: The observer was described as a female accompanied by two others.
